cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper deals with analyzing video recordings of human spermatozoa using deep learning methods. This falls under the domain of computer vision. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses deep learning methods to predict sperm motility and morphology. This falls under the domain of machine learning. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses deep learning methods to analyze and predict sperm motility and morphology. This falls under the domain of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with analyzing video recordings of human spermatozoa. This falls under the domain of multimedia. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper uses neural networks to predict sperm motility and morphology. This falls under the domain of neural computing.
